<h3>1. Click on the "Take Quiz" link to take up a quiz <br/>
2.	Click on the select course button to get your course details <br/>
3.	Select the course from the dropdown menu <br/>
4.	Click on the select assessment button to get the assessments <br/>
5.	Next, select the assessment/quiz which you want to take from the dropdown menu<br/>
6.	Start the assessment by clicking on the Start quiz button<br/>
a.	Check Your Browser Options before the Test to ensure that it is not set to disconnect after several minutes of inactivity. <br/>
b.	Don't close the window of the test for any reason. <br/>
c.	If something goes wrong, send an e-mail to the instructor immediately, documenting the exact problem and asking how to proceed.<br/>
d.	Review answers before Submitting the Quiz. Make sure you have not accidentally changed your response to a question or made a typographic mistake. <br/>
e.	Once you finish the test, click on Submit button at the bottom <br/>
f.	You will be redirected to you home page<br/>
7.	To view scores, click on View Scores link. Click on Print Result to view scores for all your courses. <br/>
8.	To logout, click on logout button


</h3>
